room_title: Escape room "Escape from Summer Vacation" by School of Hard Locks in Oceanside
room_description: Summer vacation is over. At least in 2016. But on that fateful day for the students at SoHL in March 1970, their summer vacation plans were just beginning. Where should we go? What will we see? Do we have the equipment we need? And most importantly - will we ever get out of Geography class to begin our journey? Or will we have to send an expedition team to come and find you?
